-0531_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="6776f2946697aa55489f5662d62cb9d0"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250531/bkn-20250531160725664-0531_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31943489&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1320492967683adc5f7dc010_57722477"/><published>2025-05-31T18:06:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>60fa8bd158f683b54899c382b765b9b7</id><title>銀主「2字頭」推拍市區兩房私樓 呎價唔使6500元...</title><updated>2025-05-31T18:10:02+08:00</updated><author><name>新25</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-31T18:10:02+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572642414"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572642414"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16267476" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572642414" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250531/20250531_df86b9f6a791508dafdbyMRRSdBtuv2N.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/ff5b46/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250531/20250531_df86b9f6a791508dafdbyMRRSdBtuv2N.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16267476_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16267476&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (303.58 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-31 18:10&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;銀主決心出貨套現，僅以「2字頭」推拍設有電梯的市區兩房私樓單位，呎價唔使6,500港元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-c